Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯利克教主輔佐官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們特殊警察「狩人」奉大臣的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(425.06,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前來執行保護你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到被稱為帝國最強的艾斯德斯將軍會親自前來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比這更安心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經接收到「夜襲」潛入的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(440.96,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們狩殺他們之前 就借你幾個房間來居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必我府上一定不會讓各位覺得無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對他們完全沒有興趣 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是想見見從剛剛開始 一直窺視我們的那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是被您發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾個人正是帝國派來幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓我掌握教團暴力的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇拳寺羅剎四鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想他們怎麼沒在帝都 原來是來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了將軍前來護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下原本這些專任護衛的惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也能把他們用在進攻上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和「夜襲」戰鬥沒有帝具的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(337.08,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們試過憑藉自己的實力打倒過帝具使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管帝具的能力有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其使用者終究只是肉體凡胎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也就是說 肯定有很多戰勝他們的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅剎四鬼是大臣私人僱傭的處罰人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如他們所說 他們的本領是鐵板釘釘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們只要在府邸裡悠閒地喝酒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也是 無論有多輝煌的實績
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害 不愧是艾斯德斯將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快要迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都將這幾個重要的棋子部署在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻還讓我也來到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大臣那傢伙 似乎非常重視這個宗教團體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我能再早點趕過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波魯斯先生也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明明還有妻子和女兒在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟要怎麼報告才好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是威爾之所以會被打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是為了保護黑瞳小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長也決定這次的事件既往不咎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你的心情 但你先冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生說她能堅持到現在 應該沒有生命的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我試著解剖回收來的刺客的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還不能查明其來歷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是帝具使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該「夜襲」其中一員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(382.66,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 總之那惡人的屍體拿來餵小可可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑…黑瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息了一下 好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本恢復過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的要害可是被扎中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我陪你繼續同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所見 我還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你要跟過來 你就得好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十分鐘之後 出發前往傑洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然還是在勉強自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是不要參與戰線的戰鬥比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去跟隊長說一說 讓她給你脫離任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗殺部隊的人 一旦被判定無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會連同以封口為由 處理掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什！？處理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果脫離「狩人」的話 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(405.98,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有告訴隊長 她一定會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣是不行的 我必須要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不要被處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是為了那樣死去 才誕生於世的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死 也是要在戰鬥中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我的同伴們那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要傷口癒合的話 就能完全恢復如初的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說在這種離帝都那麼遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會張貼大家的通緝令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定「狩人」會在這裡新派發呢 切記掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(255.763,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才剛說完 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是神經繃得那麼緊 也會很危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們表現出那樣的氣氛 對方也是能察覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是再自然一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明切爾茜死了 他明明是那麼悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經平復下來 全心投入新的任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成長了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這也有一些道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 這是帝都裡沒有的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這裡的人比帝都的人更有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧有地下資源和宗教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗教？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎很賺錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然最終大部分的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因為歐尼斯特大臣從中操作 都納入他囊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 他們不知道自己被人利用著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道真相的反對派 都被伯利克鎮壓住無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就需要我們作為突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先好好了解這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 接下來就去外圍逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好 聖堂附近的危險地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給自告奮勇的拉伯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這城市就像迷宮一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過人這麼多 方便混入探索 真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我的名字面貌都沒暴露過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹底搜索 提高我在娜傑塔心裡的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉伯 你做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 朱天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的行動像不像在查探周圍的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的直覺說他就是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的腳步才是最可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是經歷過眾多修羅場的人的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他似乎有所注意 但我能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就是敵人呢 去把他殺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說錯了 馬頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是「解放他的靈魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據調查 在這個墓地的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有地下通道接通聖堂和伯利克的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道通道的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來就能去到伯利克的宅邸的地下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很難找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這裡這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下通道亦有可能部署了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我沒發現你嗎 赤瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棘 你來傑洛克了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓我高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都在暗殺部隊的時候幾乎沒說過話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是在最後的決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗殺大臣時才會和你們羅剎四鬼對陣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛了帝國的壞孩子要打屁屁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬送！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們羅剎四鬼不僅進行了慘烈的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還喝著棲息於寺院後山的水怪克拉做的湯成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們能自由操縱身體！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 居然突然襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子 你就只會四處逃竄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 已經死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太沒勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 快點離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那拳我用身上的線織鎧甲擋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脈搏也用「交叉之尾」進入身體綁住血管 讓其停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果只是不必在意的雜魚啊 真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走 你還要我裝死裝到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 朱天 另一個人去你那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也是叛亂分子的密探
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是原本要和我匯合的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒法救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然身為密探 你也應該做好這種覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是現世的迷途羔羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來解放你的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你盡情高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能對女性同伴見死不救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脈搏應該已經停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太笨了 明明你一直裝死就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 考慮到自己的職務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直極力迴避正面戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要是遇到必須要戰鬥的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是會戰到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個一起放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那把刀真不祥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「村雨」倒是和你般配嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 赤瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了我進行過慘烈的修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 沒收帝具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這刀是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成你的目標就是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才故意放開帝具的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你剛才說「村雨」是不祥的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就覺得你們相性不合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不受這把被詛咒的刀的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定你應該慶幸自己的罪孽還不重 棘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是個危險的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷襲行不通嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「狩人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424.757,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認「夜襲」的赤瞳潛入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(381.6,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的職責是偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經清楚地見識到你的「村雨」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅剎四鬼加上「狩人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(502.743,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家都沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼放馬過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不已經展開絲線開始攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來解放你的靈魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇拳寺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百裂拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 我可沒叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真靈巧的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那絲線是帝具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你是「夜襲」的一員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457.314,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這次就打碎你的頭顱 徹底殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種受歡迎的形式 真想求放過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的絲線啊 捆集起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起舞吧 離心力！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這招式太大破綻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不見得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超奧義「絲線衝擊」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點程度就叫是絕招 別讓人發笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎 我的目的已經達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你們的後面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我也在此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓那個女人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才特意用那誇張的演技來吸引我們的注意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有你一個 也要解放你的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎 這麼氣勢洶洶地追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的絲線據稱是用棲息在東海雲層上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超危險種的體毛製造而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別保護要害的體毛 是極為堅韌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這部分體毛做成的絲線 實在是過於鋒利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被稱為「界斷絲」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我珍藏的一根 即使是你也切不斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這經過重重修行的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會被這些傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和身體有多強壯沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被「交叉之尾」刺中胸部的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲線就會朝你的心臟割去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來心臟部分沒經過鍛鍊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能打倒朱天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下我要被大臣責罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你不用擔這個心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然帝具被你看到了 就不能讓你活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒什麼抱歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是殺手的話這是很正常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這液體怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為液體的重量導致絲線變鬆垮 發揮不了作用！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說這是油 應該說是我的汗液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅剎四鬼很擅長這樣的身體操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話防禦結界就起不了作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站…站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再受到攻擊的話 我必死無疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別垂死掙扎 太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是敵人的話 早就搭訕你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不討厭你這種類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會答應你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等來世再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在匕首上綁了絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說回收絲線的話 匕首也一起跟著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了 為什麼我總是遇到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然巡看很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但像近道和暗道 還有很多要查的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才需要調查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是購物的話 走多久都沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你購物的時間太長 陪你一起逛太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？那是一般啦 一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法容忍女性購物的男人 胸襟太狹窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻嘲弄男人胸襟狹窄的女人才是胸襟狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意！我讓你好好分清上下關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟同伴分上下關係 就已經錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我注意一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請停止無謂的爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然知道我是多管閒事 但還是忍不住說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會是「安寧道」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教主大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有時會像這樣巡視街道周邊的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看得出來 你們是被紅線牽連著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以比起吵架 你們應該先互相告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為情侶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得偶爾爭吵一次也未嘗不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要和這種傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 才不要和你成為情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得你們很匹配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被選為擔任教主大人的隨從這光榮的職位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能近距離看到教主大人所引發的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你還有不淨的邪念附身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就配不起這個職位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的衣服全脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用神聖的儀式幫你淨身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 伯利克大人 有勞您了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過一點時間 就能完全掌控教團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我最大限度享受一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯利克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在進行神聖的儀式途中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關於羅剎四鬼的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅一個晚上就有三個被對方殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還是小看「夜襲」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(502.743,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然能給那群為非作歹的惡黨施予正義鐵槌的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我們「狩人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486.843,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜傑塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然途中中了你的詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡我要把你的夥伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部蹂躪掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,310)\fsp15\an8\fad(300,0)\bord1\1c&H1C1379&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(0,300,848,326)}斬斷因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,310)\fsp15\an8\fad(300,0)\bord1\1c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(0,326,848,370)}斬斷因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:57.60,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}朽ち果てるように燃ゆる月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:04.41,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}暁に沈みゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.84,OP-J,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\fs20\pos(358,444)}かお
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.84,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}造られた仮面で そっと近付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:16.16,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}信じるモノを 闇に落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:21.43,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}糸に絡まる エモノのように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.84,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}ただ ひたすらに 空を仰ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:34.86,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}繰り返される悲劇 不気味に笑う裏の顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:44.58,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}これ以上 何ひとつ 失くさないように刀を抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:50.19,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}闇に葬れ 汚れた笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:55.63,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}やり場のない怒り、放て！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:02:00.97,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}どれだけの 血と涙を流したら…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:05.98,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}祈るように 斬り裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:12.53,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}今日もアカク染め上げよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}振り返る過去はない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:15.04,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}この手 放した日から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.94,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}失うものはないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:25.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}繰り返し言い聞かせてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.82,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}静寂に漂う月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:37.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}どんな闇も 照らしてゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:42.36,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}強い光 未来へかざす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:47.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}負けたくはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}終わらない夢が 胸のざわめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:57.54,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}身体を巡って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:03.48,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}痛みさえ 今 強さになるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:08.04,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}信じた道を行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.98,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}私を突き動かす熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:21.58,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}描き続けてきた 世界へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.42,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}逝去的昔日無法復返
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:15.04,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}從鬆開雙手那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}不再有能失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:25.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}如此不斷反覆詢問
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.82,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}寂靜的水面浮映著一輪圓月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:37.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}一切的黑暗都能照亮驅散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:42.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}耀眼的光芒 照耀未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:47.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}正因不願服輸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}沒有終點的夢境與胸中的喧囂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:57.54,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}縈繞全身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:03.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}曾經的傷痛如今已化為堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:08.04,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}朝著自己相信的道路進發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.98,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}鼓勵我地這份熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:21.58,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}引導你前往描繪中的世界
